Brazil’s Anatel to Boost Oi-Telefonica Competition in Sao Paulo

-- B y   C a r l a   S i m o e s
-- 
2011-07-21T20:25:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/brazil-s-anatel-to-boost-oi-telefonica-competition-in-sao-paulo.html
Brazil ’s telecommunications
regulator, Anatel, aims to increase competition between Tele
Norte Leste Participacoes SA and  Telefonica SA (TEF)  in Sao Paulo
state, board member Joao Rezende told reporters today in
Brasilia.  Oi, the brand under which Tele Norte Leste operates, will
have up to seven years to create the infrastructure for a
broadband Internet network in the state, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carla Simoes in Brasilia Newsroom at 
 csimoes1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
